Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.core
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.ontology.data

Interface TermAnnotation

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<TermAnnotation>, Identified, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
GoGaf22Annotation, HpoGeneAnnotation, MpoGeneAnnotation
public interface TermAnnotation extends Identified, Serializable, Comparable<TermAnnotation>
A TermAnnotation links a TermId to a String label of a "world object".

For all annotated "world objects", the labels have to be unique for each object. The annotations can then be used for, e.g., feeding into the information content computation and thus into the similarity metrics computation algorithms.

Implementing classes have to properly implement hashValue() and equals() .

Author:
Manuel Holtgrewe, Sebastian Koehler
